Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Permission denied when reading system files

Solution: Some system files require sudo. Modify scripts to use sudo where needed or focus on user-accessible configs
Issue: DeepDiff not found

Solution: Ensure pip3 installation completed: pip3 install --user deepdiff
Issue: YAML parsing errors

Solution: Validate YAML syntax using: python3 -c "import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('file.yaml'))"
Issue: No drift detected when expected

Solution: Verify current capture ran after modifications: ls -lt current/
